{"tid":1405243,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"消防員二人小組構思","createTime":"2019-08-04T08:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:51:11.000Z","uid":131980,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b141fe458587de96221fb4e5469e65415b72f5e4","tid":1405243,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">頭盔:GTAo的RP消防員應該咁玩先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\nGTAo的差佬睇到又點,等食返自己既野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到琴日黃大仙市民用隻鐵盤就KO左粒催淚彈,有感其發<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfL0yWH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfL0yWH.gif&h=99d27039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關於點解隻鐵盤KO到粒催淚彈,我個人認為係因為呢個原理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3D50yWP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3D50yWP.gif&h=7b46d4e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n催淚彈成份當中有助燃劑幫助催淚彈燃燒,大量生產GAS,一CUT左氧,佢就燃燒唔到,反應自然中止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因此,我有個IDEA <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2pvG2NH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2pvG2NH.png&h=6c453beb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9nm2NJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9nm2NJ.png&h=eaae5042&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdJabF3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdJabF3.png&h=d03e2c25&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一有催淚彈大廚就直接吸蓋,等無煙就交比費達拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打返去差佬果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1:慳水慳力慳精力<br />\n2:機動性大大提升<br />\n3:環保,無限LOOP</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">停左反應都會好熱,所以一定要帶手套</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">BE CHEF, COVER, HIT AND RUN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c3092c406682a5a2fb17d7c0448cecf5681cf9db","tid":1405243,"uid":25187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:32:53.000Z","msg":"[8月5日大罷工] 我警告你地！！！千萬唔好堵塞過海渡輪！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1405172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1405172</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c10ae4a26237dd80831a340258e6ca820f2db38","tid":1405243,"uid":271369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"Fire triangle - heat + oxygen + fuel<br />\nShortest one with less oxygen, so fire extinguish quick"},{"pid":"8c257493c104fa78fee54c14da96337096f4c3e7","tid":1405243,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c10ae4a26237dd80831a340258e6ca820f2db38","tid":1405243,"uid":271369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"Fire triangle - heat + oxygen + fuel<br />\nShortest one with less oxygen, so fire extinguish quick"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2740c6543c0db159576d49f2a2c18185bbf881","tid":1405243,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc737754dbb88e6c6ab1357d219aae4ef6e8b15","tid":1405243,"uid":5487